      "content": "idk i dont want to go to the hospital, its always such a huge hassle and so expensive... and honestly i've been under so much stress at work lately. i really feel like it's just my anxiety acting up again. if i just take a strong dose of my propanolol and try to lie down in a dark room for an hour, do you think that would help settle it down? i just need to calm my heart rate.*",
